title: Joe Flacco blasts NFL's physicality crackdown: 'We signed up to get hurt'

sources.name: Yahoo Sports NFL
sources.title: Joe Flacco blasts NFL's physicality crackdown: 'We signed up to get hurt'
sources.description: Joe Flacco sounded off on the NFL's legislation of physicality in the game, from roughing the passer penalties to fines and more.
